data.description: Custom built home on over half an acre in the quiet, established Whitehurst community just outside the city limits of Fuquay-Varina! Charming 3 bedroom/2.5 bath home sits on a cul-de-sac lot and features an inviting covered front porch, entry with offset staircase, formal dining room adjacent to the eat-in kitchen with timeless white cabinetry, Stainless Steel appliances, and pantry for added storage. 2 Story family room gives an open feel with a gas log fireplace creating the perfect nostalgic feel. Owner's suite is located on the first floor with walk-in closet, dual vanity sinks, separate garden tub and a private enclosed commode. Secondary bedrooms are upstairs including a bonus room with flex space! Grid-less windows throughout brings in loads of natural light and neutral paint colors leaves room for any design or décor. Exterior deck overlooks the community pond with a convenient location between Downtown Holly Springs and Fuquay Varina Amenities!
